Add a timer
  #time/timer += [period: 16]

## Drawing

Set up drawing elements 
  x = #spaceship.x
  y = #spaceship.y
  shapes = [|shape   parameters|
            "rectangle" [x: 0 y: 0 width: 50 height: 50 fill: 0x000000 stroke: 0xFFFFFF line-width: 5]
  #spaceship/drawing = [
    shape: "path" 
    parameters: [
      start-point: [x: 0 y: 0] 
      contains: [|shape parameters| shapes] 
      translate: [x: x y: y]
      rotate: #spaceship/direction
    ]
  ]

Draw Spaceship
canvas = [
    type: "canvas"
    contains: [|shape parameters| #spaceship.drawing]
    parameters: [width: 800 height: 800]
  ]
  #html/app = [
    root: "mech-root"
    contains: [[|type contains parameters| canvas]]
  ]
